===Etymology===
Compound of {{compound|en|odd|ball}}. Attested since the 1940s, with the adjective appearing earlier than the noun.

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|US}} {{IPA|/ˈɑːdˌbɔl/|lang=en}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

